{"tid":2512633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人的無人性「中國點火VS印度點火」","createTime":"2021-05-02T01:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T02:20:45.000Z","uid":337052,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"826c4a1d1a777cebf67aa82bbb3188144356ae59","tid":2512633,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:39:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">支那人的無人性「中國點火VS印度點火」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在習近平就印度疫情向印度總理莫迪致慰問電之後，中共政法委官方微博發布一則嘲諷印度疫情的帖文，遭到印度駐華大使館的抗議，並引起軒然大波。網民評說，萬沒想到人底線這麼低，&ldquo;低到能公然嘲諷生命的流逝&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2021/05/id12918545-f9d6b37a28a0cc8b338bf3e257519b0e-e1619906841127.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2Fid12918545-f9d6b37a28a0cc8b338bf3e257519b0e-e1619906841127.jpg&h=a9183a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月1日，印度官方表示，該國當日新增401,993個確診病例。根據官方數據，印度平均每分鐘有2.5人染疫身亡。印度疫情失控之時，全球多國提供支援。<br />\n<br />\n目前，中國、美國、新加坡等20個國家和地區發現了印度變異毒株病例。外界擔憂印度疫情或危及全球。<br />\n<br />\n5月1日，<span class=\"red\">中共政法委新聞網站官方微博&ldquo;中國長安網&rdquo;發布一則題為&ldquo;中國點火VS印度點火&rdquo;的合成圖，並配有印度疫情的話題標籤，暗示&ldquo;中國點火發射火箭，印度點火焚屍火葬&rdquo;，藉此嘲諷印度疫情。</span><br />\n<br />\n該微博引發海內外社交媒體的關注和熱議，不少&ldquo;五毛&rdquo;、憤青的仇恨情緒被點燃。在&ldquo;中國長安網&rdquo;的這則微博引起印度駐華大使館的抗議之後，該微博被刪除。"},{"pid":"d9f019ecf87f3226f3c77566f4a1f6daa0429d8f","tid":2512633,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"玩火"},{"pid":"9274e933189f4e1b8c1f7cc74414631c80147316","tid":2512633,"uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"支那人是不值得同情的民族"},{"pid":"2de031f40229b48d0b1ac6400582c5e96d1a3ee5","tid":2512633,"uid":76681,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:42:48.000Z","msg":"推到比世界知，呢個仆街無人性民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fb6b5acb6f85fed07aa4500bf6601364773e13","tid":2512633,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:44:57.000Z","msg":"加速加速"},{"pid":"1378a3741447badd338eeb4229d608a5b936d0e5","tid":2512633,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:51:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中共政法委公開嘲諷印度疫情慘況 網友怒轟「泯滅人性」</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/05/02/3518165_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F05%2F02%2F3518165_1_1.jpg&h=c1bea5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國公安部新聞中心／公安部治安管理局官方微博「中國警方在線」，發佈圖片嘲笑印度疫情失控。（擷取自中國警方在線微博）"},{"pid":"872126840fc20834057d7a47a78e3b8be0115c5d","tid":2512633,"uid":238370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"咁印度都可以拎武漢黎鞭屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0495ef9e6920891cb0a8312d1d3adc43ba22d4c","tid":2512633,"uid":83713,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdG6LsjJDmeHrv8ZeJvBxMfhV4c2XBkkps8dqqHUVL6Ae?filename=V30jwHZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV30jwHZ.jpg&h=23af9d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洋人打獵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWyDodfTdSfZuU8pqprfNfiSUZFWzcwaFCLpHmdbad5ur?filename=kDCaDn0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDCaDn0.jpg&h=bbf57948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本人打獵"},{"pid":"7f415831947b2de1265b987e5e207205c21d015d","tid":2512633,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://ipfs.infura.io/ipf